value: Vous ne tenez pas le rythme ?
Votre vie touche à sa fin !
I was granted this new garb. Truth told, it doesn't matter what I wear. It's all the same to me.
*startle* Oh, it's you. Take it easy with the horseplay.
Size doesn't give one an inherent advantage in battle, but it can intimidate an opponent.
You wish to know my strength? All right then, how about we arm-wrestle?
Eirika est toujours ravie de me voir porter de nouveaux vêtements. Pourquoi donc ?
Je dois ressembler davantage à mon père. Non seulement en matière de force, mais aussi de sagesse.
I will become stronger yet. I vow to protect you.
